title: Devil's Sight
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki
xpcost: 1

You can see perfectly well in darkness and dim light, both magical (as the spell [[darkness]]) and non-magical, out to a distance of 120 feet. This ability is innate to most [[devil]]s, and is more powerful than [[darkvision]] in that darkness does not impede one's vision whatsoever.